---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import achievementsImage from "@assets/achievements.png";
import { ArrowUpRight } from "lucide-react";
import ceoImage from "@assets/ceo.png";

const lineUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_LINE_URL;
---

<section id="トップ" class="pt-16">
  <div
    class="space-y-8 bg-linear-to-b from-[#1D1C1B]/0 via-[#1D1C1B]/50 via-55% to-[#1D1C1B] p-6 text-neutral-100"
  >
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-center font-black italic">
        <span class="block">マンションオプション工事のプロが</span>
        <span class="block">住まいを最適に仕上げます</span>
      </p>
      <div class="h-[3px] bg-neutral-100"></div>
      <h2 class="text-center font-extrabold italic">
        <span class="block">
          <span class="text-5xl">必要な工事</span>
          <span class="text-3xl">だけを</span>
        </span>
        <span class="block">
          <span class="text-5xl">適正価格</span>
          <span class="text-3xl">で</span>
        </span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6 font-bold text-neutral-900">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="w-fit bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1">
          <p class="text-xs">フロアコーティング・エコカラット・収納・鏡・フィルムなど</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-fit bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1">
          <p>マンション専門スタッフが</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-fit bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 text-orange-500">
          <p>“あなたの住まいにちょうど良い工事”</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-fit bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1">
          <p>だけを最終提案。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="w-fit bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1">
          <p class="text-xs">中間マージンを排除した適正価格で、</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-fit bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 text-orange-500">
          <p>新しい暮らしに“安心”と“満足”をプラス。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Image
      src={achievementsImage}
      alt="施工実績"
      width={800}
      class="w-full"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center gap-2 overflow-x-clip bg-orange-500 py-6">
    <p class="z-10 font-bold text-neutral-100">24時間お問い合わせ可能</p>
    <a
      href={lineUrl}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="button button-outline z-10"
      data-variant="outline"
    >
      <p>LINEで簡単お問い合わせ</p>
      <div
        class="flex aspect-square h-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-orange-500 p-1 text-neutral-100"
      >
        <ArrowUpRight size={24} />
      </div>
    </a>
    <Image
      src={ceoImage}
      alt="代表者"
      width={576}
      class="absolute -right-20 bottom-0 z-0 w-72"
      loading="eager"
    />
  </div>
</section>
